de.ityx.mediatrix.data

Class Customer

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.ityx.mediatrix.data.ErpsData
      • de.ityx.mediatrix.data.Customer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IErpsData, IProjectRelation, Serializable, Comparable<Customer>

    public class Customer
extends ErpsData
implements Comparable<Customer>, IProjectRelation
    The email address from where the enquiry is sent to the system defines the customer. How to use: The customers are assigned to the project. If the many projects are bound per alias, the customer can contain the cases from the identical customer that is located in the other project.
